msgstr ""

# Description of tutorial article <a href="http://translate.khanacademy.org/college-careers-more/career-content/career-profiles-build-and-fix-things/career-profile-architectural-designer/a/what-does-an-architectural-designer-do">http://translate.khanacademy.org/college-careers-more/career-content/career-profiles-build-and-fix-things/career-profile-architectural-designer/a/what-does-an-architectural-designer-do</a>
# (KA_SOURCE_TREE: shared)
# (format: html)
#: intl/datastore:1
msgid "Learn about the responsibilities of an architectural designer and opportunities to progress in this field."
msgstr ""

# Article is at <a href="http://translate.khanacademy.org/college-careers-more/career-content/career-profiles-build-and-fix-things/career-profile-architectural-designer/a/what-does-an-architectural-designer-do">http://translate.khanacademy.org/college-careers-more/career-content/career-profiles-build-and-fix-things/career-profile-architectural-designer/a/what-does-an-architectural-designer-do</a>.
