msgid "How do you become a district representative for a state senator?"
msgstr ""

# Description of tutorial article <a href="http://translate.khanacademy.org/college-careers-more/career-content/serve-your-community/career-profile-district-representative/a/how-do-you-become-a-district-representative-for-a-state-senator">http://translate.khanacademy.org/college-careers-more/career-content/serve-your-community/career-profile-district-representative/a/how-do-you-become-a-district-representative-for-a-state-senator</a>
# (KA_SOURCE_TREE: shared)
# (format: html)
#: intl/datastore:1
msgid "Learn about steps you can take to enter the world of politics as a district representative for a state senator.&nbsp;"
msgstr ""

# Article is at <a href="http://translate.khanacademy.org/college-careers-more/career-content/serve-your-community/career-profile-district-representative/a/how-do-you-become-a-district-representative-for-a-state-senator">http://translate.khanacademy.org/college-careers-more/career-content/serve-your-community/career-profile-district-representative/a/how-do-you-become-a-district-representative-for-a-state-senator</a>.
# (KA_SOURCE_TREE: shared)
# (format: perseus_text)
#: intl/datastore:1
msgid "For most jobs in politics, building relationships and experience is often more important than pursuing a specific degree. There is not one set path to become a district representative for a state senator, but the following practices can help you gain a foothold in this field. "
msgstr ""

# Article is at <a href="http://translate.khanacademy.org/college-careers-more/career-content/serve-your-community/career-profile-district-representative/a/how-do-you-become-a-district-representative-for-a-state-senator">http://translate.khanacademy.org/college-careers-more/career-content/serve-your-community/career-profile-district-representative/a/how-do-you-become-a-district-representative-for-a-state-senator</a>.
# (KA_SOURCE_TREE: shared)
# (format: perseus_text)
#: intl/datastore:1
msgid "Gain hands on experience by volunteering for a local representative or helping with a campaign. Giving your time shows your dedication and is seen as paying your dues. Newly elected officials often hire campaign volunteers to move into paid staff positions. Even if your volunteer experience doesn’t turn into an immediate job offer, you’re still building relationships that can open doors down the road.  "
msgstr ""

# Article is at <a href="http://translate.khanacademy.org/college-careers-more/career-content/serve-your-community/career-profile-district-representative/a/how-do-you-become-a-district-representative-for-a-state-senator">http://translate.khanacademy.org/college-careers-more/career-content/serve-your-community/career-profile-district-representative/a/how-do-you-become-a-district-representative-for-a-state-senator</a>.
# (KA_SOURCE_TREE: shared)
# (format: perseus_text)
#: intl/datastore:1
msgid "Gaining a job as a district representative does not require a particular license or degree; however, focusing on your education will help you develop important skills for this role. If you are currently in high school or college, take classes that will help broaden your perspective on issues, such as cultural studies, sociology, and psychology. Communications classes can also help prepare you to interact with diverse groups within your community. Aim to earn a bachelor’s degree at minimum. "
msgstr ""

# Article is at <a href="http://translate.khanacademy.org/college-careers-more/career-content/serve-your-community/career-profile-district-representative/a/how-do-you-become-a-district-representative-for-a-state-senator">http://translate.khanacademy.org/college-careers-more/career-content/serve-your-community/career-profile-district-representative/a/how-do-you-become-a-district-representative-for-a-state-senator</a>.
# (KA_SOURCE_TREE: shared)
# (format: perseus_text)
#: intl/datastore:1
msgid "If you know you want to work as a district representative for a state senator, consider calling the district office. Ask if it would be possible to intern in order to gain experience and learn more about the role. While some political internships are advertised, don’t be afraid to ask about opportunities that aren’t directly posted. Showing initiative is key to advancing in politics. "
msgstr ""

# Article is at <a href="http://translate.khanacademy.org/college-careers-more/career-content/serve-your-community/career-profile-district-representative/a/how-do-you-become-a-district-representative-for-a-state-senator">http://translate.khanacademy.org/college-careers-more/career-content/serve-your-community/career-profile-district-representative/a/how-do-you-become-a-district-representative-for-a-state-senator</a>.
# (KA_SOURCE_TREE: shared)
# (format: perseus_text)
#: intl/datastore:1
msgid "“[Working in Politics](https://www.bls.gov/careeroutlook/2008/summer/art01.pdf).” U.S. Bureau of Labor Statistics. Occupational Outlook Quarterly. Summer 2008. "
msgstr ""

